unittitle_ssm: Iraq, Egypt, Yemen - compiled by L. Wells - Hisham Khatib Collection
abstract_ssm: Created by officer Les Wells while he served with the Medical Service at the RAF General Hospital in Hinaidi as part of the "British Forces in Iraq" RAF Command and whilst he was stationed in Egypt between 1934 and 1936 - part of the Hisham Khatib Collection.
